cs.NI, cs.RO, cs.SY, cs.IT, cs.MM

Reasoning: 
- cs.NI (Networking and Internet Architecture) is the most likely category as the paper focuses on a cellular networking scenario and proposes algorithms to improve the spectral efficiency of the network. 
- cs.RO (Robotics) is also likely as the paper deals with the mobility of drones and proposes drone mobility algorithms. 
- cs.SY (Systems and Control) is another possible category as the paper deals with the control of drone movements to optimize network performance. 
- cs.IT (Information Theory) is a possible category as the paper deals with improving the efficiency of wireless communication. 
- cs.MM (Multimedia) is a less likely category, but still possible as the paper deals with improving packet throughput in a wireless network.
